# Fix Game Progress & UI Alignment

## Problem
1. **Match Result Roadblock**: The user is unable to swipe or click on the match result card because the `_isProcessing` flag, set during the final scenario of the week, is never reset before the match result card is shown.
2. **UI Overflow**: Elements like "Match Odds" and "Logos" require scrolling on most screens, leading to a fragmented experience.

## Proposed Changes

### [Fix] Game Logic
#### [MODIFIED] [game_screen.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart)
- Reset `_isProcessing = false` in [_triggerReelResult](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#419-472) to ensure the match result card is interactive.

### [UI] Layout Optimization
#### [MODIFIED] [game_screen.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart)
- **Audio Removal**: Completely disable the [AudioManager](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/utils/audio_manager.dart#4-83) implementation. It will now be a dummy class that returns immediately from all calls. This eliminates `audioplayers` as a potential source of native browser crashes.
- **Resource Hardening**: Double-check all [Timer](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#217-233) and `AnimationController` usage in [GameScreen](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#22-28) and [BreakingNewsTicker](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/breaking_news_ticker.dart#5-11) to ensure they are strictly tied to the widget lifecycle.
- **Null Safety**: Add extra null checks in the UI for `nextOpponent` and `activeScenario` values.
- **Compact Table**: Reduce font sizes and padding in [_verticalTable](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#812-924).
- **Merged Stats & Manager**: Tighten the [_statsRow](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#596-666) layout to use less vertical space.
- **Dynamic Sizing**: Adjust card dimensions and spacing to ensure bottom elements (Odds, Ticker) are visible on standard mobile screens without excessive scrolling.
- **Broadcast Hub**: Move match odds closer to the main layout to reduce the need for scrolling.

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Play through a full week and verify that the match result card can be swiped.
- Check the UI layout on different aspect ratios in the browser/emulator to ensure "Match Odds" are visible without scrolling.
